  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nThis may not be straightforward to implement, so feel free to close if this is not doable. But intuitively I'd expect this to stay as-is:\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\n// Handle ETH.\r\nif (msg.value > 0) IWETH(asset).deposit{value: msg.value}();\r\n// Handle WETH.\r\nelse IERC20(asset).safeTransferFrom(msg.sender, address(this), amt);\r\n```\r\n\r\nCurrently it gets changed to:\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\n// Handle ETH.\r\nif (msg.value > 0) {\r\n  IWETH(asset).deposit{value: msg.value}();\r\n}\r\n// Handle WETH.\r\nelse {\r\n  IERC20(asset).safeTransferFrom(msg.sender, address(this), amt);\r\n}\r\n```\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
